The '''Conference of Uncommitted Worlds''' ([[0 ABY/Legends|0 ABY]]), held on [[Kabal/Legends|Kabal]] just after the [[Battle of Yavin/Legends|Battle of Yavin]], was a gathering where [[Princess/Legends|Princess]] [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa]] secured a commitment by [[Silver Fyre/Legends|Silver Fyre]] to aid the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Alliance to Restore the Republic]]. Fyre's deputy commander, [[Kraaken]], secretly alerted the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]] to the conference, resulting in an [[Raid on Kabal|assault]] on Kabal by [[TIE/sa tactical bomber/Legends|TIE Bombers]].

